settings.title: Videographer Kevin Wolf’s Advice for Aspiring Creators
settings.text: As a self-proclaimed adrenaline lover, Kevin knows the difference quality tech protection makes. We asked him to share a list of his must-haves for his travel kit. Here’s what he listed...

settings.title: IMPACTHERO™. The Hero Your Tech Deserves.
settings.text: Calling all Android users! There’s a new hero ready to protect your tech. Meet IMPACTHERO™, an innovative new case for Android with the ability to survive an eight-foot fall.

settings.title: Take a Peek: Meet the New iPhone SE 2022 and 5th Generation iPad Air 2022
settings.text: On March 8th, Apple announced the launch of the highly anticipated iPhone SE 2022 at their Peek Performance event. For everything you need to know about the new devices, take a peek at the breakdown so you can decide how to upgrade.

settings.title: NEW RELEASE ALERT: Samsung Galaxy S22, Galaxy S22+, Galaxy S22 Ultra
settings.text: With a new year comes a new Samsung Unpacked Event, and this year did not disappoint. On February 9th, Samsung revealed the new Samsung S22, their most iconic and note-worthy device yet.

settings.title: Essentials for 2022: Protect Your Tech with the Best
settings.text: New Year ready? Put your best foot forward in 2022 with these essentials, including the perfect cases for all your tech. If 2021 taught us anything, it’s that we are resilient and can do anything – so your tech and cases should too.
